  <summary date="2021-07-20T18:59:04Z" status="Introduced in House">Supporting Apprenticeship Colleges Act of 2021

This bill directs the Department of Education to award grants to institutions of higher education that sponsor construction and manufacturing-oriented registered apprenticeship programs for (1) expanding or supporting outreach to high schools, local businesses, and local workforce development boards; and (2) providing advising and support services to students who are enrolled in these apprenticeship programs.</summary>
